They've been waiting for you
at Duval's all day.

663
00:48:05,468 --> 00:48:08,385
I had no idea. Nobody told me.

664
00:48:08,512 --> 00:48:11,383
We've been calling you
on the telephone for hours.

665
00:48:13,308 --> 00:48:18,053
I've been at the café all day.
I'm terribly sorry.

666
00:48:18,188 --> 00:48:21,354
I don't want to sound like
the personnel department,

667
00:48:21,482 --> 00:48:24,852
but you ought to get to bed early.
The camera picks up everything.

668
00:48:24,986 --> 00:48:28,022
I don't want to spend my life
retouching your pictures.

669
00:48:28,156 --> 00:48:32,070
When we're done, you can spend
all your time making small talk.

670
00:48:32,201 --> 00:48:36,412
Small talk? I suppose you think
the neckline of a dress

671
