meets the President.

679
00:49:03,562 --> 00:49:06,896
An invitation to Flostre's home
is a great honour,

680
00:49:07,024 --> 00:49:09,479
and as hard to get
as an invitation to...

681
00:49:09,610 --> 00:49:11,353
The White House.

682
00:49:11,486 --> 00:49:14,238
I don't think jokes about Flostre
are funny.

683
00:49:14,364 --> 00:49:17,779
No more jokes. But let's be friendly.
We have to work together.

684
00:49:17,909 --> 00:49:22,202
You don't have to be friendly
to work together. Acquainted will do.

685
00:49:22,329 --> 00:49:24,618
Am I supposed to
go over to Duval's now?

686
00:49:24,748 --> 00:49:26,575
