693
00:49:43,557 --> 00:49:47,554
I don't want you spending
your life retouching my pictures.

694
00:49:47,685 --> 00:49:49,428
You are mad, aren't you?

695
00:49:51,439 --> 00:49:53,265
No, I'm not mad, I...

